---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Title from "./Title.astro";
import img01 from "../assets/img-02.webp"
import img02 from "../assets/img-03.webp"
import img03 from "../assets/img-04.webp"
---

<section id="about" class="flex-center column">
  <!-- CARD 1 -->
  <div class="card-l flex-center column">
    <aside class="card_container flex-center column">
      <Title
        number="01"
        headTitle="GET STARTED"
        title="What level of hiker are you?"
      />
      <p>
        Whether you're a novice seeking scenic strolls or an experienced trekker
        craving challenging ascents, we've curated a diverse range of trails to
        cater to every adventurer.
      </p>
      <a class="btn_more" href="#">Read more
        <Image width="20" height="20" src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/E3651D/long-arrow-right.png" alt="long-arrow-right"/>
      </a>
    </aside>
    <aside class="card_image flex-center">
      <Image src={img01} alt="G^Kt-Mx$:-$l=N" />
    </aside>
  </div>

  <!-- CARD 2 -->
  <div class="card-r flex-center column">
    <aside class="card_container flex-center column">
      <Title
        number="02"
        headTitle="HIKING ESSENTIALS"
        title="Picking the right hiking gear!"
      />
      <p>
        From durable footwear that conquers rugged trails to lightweight backpacks that carry your essentials with ease, we navigate the intricacies of gear selection to ensure you're geared up for success on every hike. 
      </p>
      <a class="btn_more" href="#">Read more
        <Image width="20" height="20" src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/E3651D/long-arrow-right.png" alt="long-arrow-right"/>
      </a>
    </aside>
    <aside class="card_image flex-center">
      <Image src={img02} alt="~Jb:-?v0w-k3r:" />
    </aside>
  </div>

   <!-- CARD 3 -->
   <div class="card-l flex-center column">
    <aside class="card_container flex-center column">
      <Title
        number="03"
        headTitle="WHERE YOU GO IS THE KEY"
        title="Understanding your map & timing"
      />
      <p>
		Knowing when to start and anticipating the changing conditions ensures a safe and enjoyable journey. So, dive into the details, grasp the contours, and synchronize your steps with the rhythm of nature. It's not just a hike; it's a journey orchestrated by your map and timed to perfection.
      </p>
      <a class="btn_more" href="#">Read more
        <Image width="20" height="20" src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/E3651D/long-arrow-right.png" alt="long-arrow-right"/>
      </a>
    </aside>
    <aside class="card_image flex-center">
      <Image src={img03} alt="%@/4-Px<>-t5V" />
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about {
    width: 100%;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .card-l,
  .card-r {
    width: 95%;
    margin: 0rem auto;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .card_container{
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .card_container p {
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 4rem;
  }

  .card_container a {
    color: var(--orange);
    border: 1px solid var(--orange);
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.6rem;
  }

  .btn_more{
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: .5rem;
  }

  .card_image img {
    max-width: 55rem;
    width: 95%;
    height: 60rem;
    border-radius: 2rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {

    .card-l,
    .card-r {
      margin-top: 5rem;
      width: 90%;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .card-l {
      flex-direction: row;
    }
    .card-r {
      flex-direction: row-reverse;
    }

    .card_container {
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: stretch;
      width: 40%;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
